Author: Morgan6788
Text: Eugenia Cooney hadn't been to a doctor in years and wasn't diagnosed until she almost died. I guess all that time she didn't have a disorder/s

Author: grumpygrumbles
Text: Yeah, that is annoying. Like it’s hard to pinpoint exactly what your disorder is without a professional eye on it but that doesn’t negate the fact that one has one?? Plus, Dx only technically exists in the context of treatment. They weren’t created under any rule that they don’t exist without meeting the criteria or whatever.   that would piss me off too lol my ED was arguably much worse before I sought out treatment soooo
